\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 0.9999999996689439, \"rank\": 3.310766065869911e-10, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vakhtang Kipshidze, the deputy chairman of the Russian Orthodox Church's Synodal Department for Church Relations with Society and the Media, expressed outrage over a performance during the ceremony that depicted the \\\"Last Supper\\\" with a drag queen.\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 1047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vakhtang_VI_of_Kartli\", \"score\": 0.7760630793381748, \"rank\": 0.276316231128285, \"text\": \"Vakhtang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vakhtang_VI_of_Kartli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vakhtang_VI_of_Kartli\"}, {\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Orthodox_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999486135507, \"rank\": 3.871891113266304e-08, \"text\": \"Russian Orthodox Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Orthodox_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Orthodox_Church\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kipshidze also noted that the Russian flag was banned from being carried in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Russia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If this demonic display had taken place under the shadow of our flag, it would not have been possible to experience a great joy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Expressing solidarity with millions of Christians who felt insulted by the opening ceremony, Kipshidze said: \\\"Those who directed the Olympic opening showed their disdain for European civilization and Christianity as its foundation.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.7668401251822332, \"rank\": 0.21487533663782413, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_culture\", \"score\": 0.9916672280692428, \"rank\": 0.00627442633787438, \"text\": \"European civilization\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9562833061137694, \"rank\": 0.04560803396557418, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is sad to see a culture based on godlessness growing in the center of Europe, parodying Christianity just as a monkey parodies a human being.\\\"\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9562833061137694, \"rank\": 0.04560803396557418, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"History  Editorial Guidelines  Social Media Policies  Executive Team  Domestic Offices  International Offices  Logo